org.apache.calcite.plan.hep

Class HepRelVertex

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.rel.AbstractRelNode
      • org.apache.calcite.plan.hep.HepRelVertex
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, RelOptNode, RelNode

    public class HepRelVertex
extends AbstractRelNode
    HepRelVertex wraps a real RelNode as a vertex in a DAG representing the entire query expression.

      • computeSelfCost

        public RelOptCost computeSelfCost(RelOptPlanner planner,
                                  RelMetadataQuery mq)
        Description copied from interface: RelNode
        Returns the cost of this plan (not including children). The base implementation throws an error; derived classes should override.

        NOTE jvs 29-Mar-2006: Don't call this method directly. Instead, use RelMetadataQuery.getNonCumulativeCost(org.apache.calcite.rel.RelNode), which gives plugins a chance to override the rel's default ideas about cost.
